Oregon Country (1804-10-01)

1804/10/01 -> 1846/06/14

Based on American exploration of the Northwest, the United States claimed the Oregon Country, an area west of the 1803 Louisiana Purchase that was not specifically defined.

(Hayes, 97-100, 131-138; Paullin, 36-37, pl. 49)
